<view><view class="column bf mt20 mb2"><view class="item f-r">优惠券名</view><view class="item4"><input class="w80" placeholder="填写优惠券名称，不超过14个字" placeholder-class="pl-class" maxlength="14" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','title','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{title}}" bindinput="__e"/></view></view><view class="column bf mb2"><view class="item f-r">面额</view><view class="item4"><picker value="{{index}}" range="{{pricelist}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['bindPickerChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="select">{{pricelist[index]+" 元"}}</view></picker></view></view><view class="column bf mb2"><view class="item f-r">消费金额</view><view class="item4 f-l"><input class="fl w30 fc" placeholder="消费金额" type="digit" placeholder-class="pl-class" maxlength="5" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','t_limit','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{t_limit}}" bindinput="__e"/>元</view></view><view class="column bf mb2"><view class="item f-r">有效期限</view><view class="item4"><picker mode="date" value="{{date}}" start="{{startDate}}" end="{{endDate}}" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['bindDateChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><view class="select">{{date}}</view></picker></view></view><view class="column bf mb2"><view class="item f-r">发放数量</view><view class="item4 f-l"><input class="fl w15 fc" placeholder="1" type="number" placeholder-class="pl-class" maxlength="4" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','total','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{total}}" bindinput="__e"/>张</view></view><view class="column bf mb2"><view class="item f-r">每人限领</view><view class="item4 f-l"><input class="fl w15 fc" placeholder="1" type="number" placeholder-class="pl-class" maxlength="4" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','eachlimit','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{eachlimit}}" bindinput="__e"/>张</view></view><view class="tips"><text>提交后仅可删除无法修改，请确认设置正确；
		每次消费仅可使用1张优惠券。</text></view><button class="btn mt40 mb20" disabled="{{logining}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['formSubmit',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">确认提交</button></view>